(gdb) x/[len]a [addr]
(gdb) x/[N]c [addr]  打印 N 个字符
(gdb) x/1s [addr]  打印字符串
以二进制打印addr1~addr2的内存
(gdb) dump binary memory result.bin [addr1] [addr2]


