五、同版本升级
1.主备节点/etc/storware/storware.conf下same_ver_upgrade = no的配置项改为 same_ver_upgrade = yes，然后重启下服务supervisorctl  restart  all

2.然后在重启apache2服务：  service  apache2  restart即可

